OL,3,CRival protests underway in London as
OL,4,Cmassive police operation in place
OL,6,FSaturday could end up being one of the
OL,7,Fmost challenging days for the Met
OL,8,FPolice in its history, ITV News
OL,9,FCorrespondent John Ray reports
OL,11,FThousands of people have descended on
OL,12,FLondon for two major demonstrations
OL,13,Famid a huge #4.5 million police
OL,14,Foperation.
OL,16,FPolice have estimated that about
OL,17,F50,000 people are set to attend Tommy
OL,18,FRobinson's Unite the Kingdom march,
OL,19,Fwhile 30,000 are expected to go to the
OL,20,Fpro-Palestine Nakba Day rally.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
