OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779055867
OL,3,CRival protests underway in London as
OL,4,Cmassive police operation in place
OL,6,FArmoured vehicles, police horses,
OL,7,Fdogs, drones and helicopters will be
OL,8,Fdeployed along with around 4,000
OL,9,Fofficers on duty as the Met aims to
OL,10,Favoid clashes between the two rallies.
OL,12,FTens of thousands of people have
OL,13,Fgathered for the Unite the Kingdom
OL,14,Fmarch, many waving Union flags, while
OL,15,Fprotesters in South Kensington are
OL,16,Fcarrying Palestine flags and signs
OL,17,Freading "smash the far right" for the
OL,18,Fpro-Palestine rally.
OL,26,@yD@IOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
