OL,3,CRival protests underway in London as
OL,4,Cmassive police operation in place
OL,6,FChants of "we want Starmer out" could
OL,7,Fbe heard on Kingsway from the Unite
OL,8,Fthe Kingdom march.
OL,10,FOn Saturday Met Police said as of 1pm,
OL,11,F11 people had been arrested "for a
OL,12,Fvariety of offences" at the Unite the
OL,13,FKingdom and Nakba Day protests.
OL,15,FMr Robinson posted on X on Saturday
OL,16,Fmorning saying "today, we Unite The
OL,17,FKingdom and the West in the greatest
OL,18,Fpatriotic display the world has ever
OL,19,Fseen".
OL,26,@nD@KOUnD@_O]sD@]OUtD@TO]xD@POU{D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
