OL,3,CRival protests underway in London as
OL,4,Cmassive police operation in place
OL,6,F"They do not reflect the Britain I'm
OL,7,Fproud of. Peaceful protest is a
OL,8,Ffundamental right and one I will
OL,9,Falways protect.
OL,11,F"But if protest turns violent, we will
OL,12,Fact swiftly, with extra court capacity
OL,13,Fin place."
OL,15,FTwo men who arrived in London to
OL,16,Fattend the Unite the Kingdom protest
OL,17,Fhave been arrested in the vicinity of
OL,18,FEuston station over an unrelated
OL,19,Fincident in Birmingham, police said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@JO]
