OL,3,CRival protests underway in London as
OL,4,Cmassive police operation in place
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police posted on X
OL,7,Fsaying: "Two men, wanted on suspicion
OL,8,Fof GBH following an incident in
OL,9,FBirmingham where a man was run over,
OL,10,Fwere spotted arriving into London to
OL,11,Fattend the UTK protest."
OL,13,FProsecutors have been told to consider
OL,14,Fwhether protest placards, banners and
OL,15,Fchants viewed on social media may
OL,16,Famount to offences of stirring up
OL,17,Fhatred during the rallies.
OL,26,@oD@IOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
