OL,3,CRival protests underway in London as
OL,4,Cmassive police operation in place
OL,6,FThe new guidance, issued before what
OL,7,Fpolice have described as an
OL,8,F"unprecedented" security operation,
OL,9,Furges prosecutors to assess whether
OL,10,Fslogans, symbols or chants may
OL,11,Finfluence audiences online if they are
OL,12,Ffilmed and shared.
OL,14,FThe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,15,Fsaid the revised advice is designed to
OL,16,Freflect "the changing international
OL,17,Fcontext" and follows separate guidance
OL,18,Fconcerning the fast-tracking of hate
OL,19,Fcrime prosecutions issued earlier this
OL,20,Fmonth.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@OO]xD@IOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
