OL,3,CRival protests underway in London as
OL,4,Cmassive police operation in place
OL,6,FThe guidance tells prosecutors to take
OL,7,Faccount of the wider context surrou
OL,9,Fnding protests, including heightened
OL,10,Ftensions linked to national or
OL,11,Finternational events.
OL,13,FRecent criminal cases have seen
OL,14,Fsuspects charged after shouting "death
OL,15,Fto the IDF (Israel Defence Forces)"
OL,16,Fand "globalise the intifada".
OL,26,@vD@aOUwD@cO]xD@EOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
