OL,3,CRival protests underway in London as
OL,4,Cmassive police operation in place
OL,6,FDirector of Public Prosecutions
OL,7,FStephen Parkinson said "this is not
OL,8,Fabout restricting free speech" and "it
OL,9,Fis about preventing hate crime and
OL,10,Fprotecting the public, particularly at
OL,11,Fa time of heightened tensions".
OL,13,FThe government has also blocked 11
OL,14,Fforeign nationals described by Sir
OL,15,FKeir Starmer as "far-right agitators"
OL,16,Ffrom entering the UK ahead of the
OL,17,FUnite the Kingdom rally.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@^O]pD@dOUsD@^O]wD@QOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
