OL,3,CRival protests underway in London as
OL,4,Cmassive police operation in place
OL,6,FSpeaking during a visit to a
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police command centre in
OL,8,FLambeth on Friday, the prime minister
OL,9,Fsaid the Unite the Kingdom organisers
OL,10,Fwere "peddling hatred and division,
OL,11,Fplain and simple".
OL,13,FMet Commissioner Sir Mark Rowley was
OL,14,Falso at the visit and told Sir Keir:
OL,15,F"We've got a time when hate crime has
OL,16,Fbeen escalated for the last two or
OL,17,Fthree years."
OL,26,@rD@FOUsD@QO]wD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
