OL,3,CRival protests underway in London as
OL,4,Cmassive police operation in place
OL,6,FMetropolitan Police Deputy Assistant
OL,7,FCommissioner James Harman said the
OL,8,Fpolicing operation will cost the force
OL,9,F#4.5 million, with #1.7 million being
OL,10,Fused on bringing in officers from
OL,11,Fother forces to boost numbers.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, the Metropolitan Police
OL,14,FFederation said many officers have had
OL,15,Fleave cancelled and rest days
OL,16,Fwithdrawn to meet policing
OL,17,Frequirements, adding: "There are not
OL,18,Fenough of us."
OL,26,@yD@WOUzD@NO]
